## 9. Recommended System Roles

## 9.1 The application backend

The backend should:

- verify the admin user
- decide which workflow is being run
- choose which MCP tools are allowed
- create generation job records
- call the Responses API
- validate the response format
- save draft outputs and metadata
- return results to the admin UI

## 9.2 The MCP server

The MCP server should:

- expose business tools only
- validate auth and permissions
- return safe, scoped data
- avoid becoming a giant copy of your backend
- remain modular and auditable

## 9.3 Firestore

Firestore should remain the operational source of truth for:

- templates
n- generation jobs
- generated versions
- final approved documents
- AI logs
- audit trails

